{"tid":2162842,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"2020 FG 搵工更加難, 同時亦更加考大家準備功夫有無做足 [過來人分享]","createTime":"2020-08-18T10:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T16:01:34.000Z","uid":334720,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"08dc64a0c803af165901e2a889b418ba71597027","tid":2162842,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:29:10.000Z","msg":"一定要plan好自己career 目標 &amp; 方向 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好盲頭烏蠅咁去apply, 變左哂時間, 尤其是今年競爭更加大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望幫到手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\">例如d人想做marketing<br />\n咁係marketing邊個範疇? </span><br />\nDigital Marketing<br />\nSocial Media Marketing <br />\nMarketing Communication (MarCom) / Content Marketing<br />\nBrand Marketing / PR個類<br />\nResearch marketing<br />\n<br />\n每個範疇已經係好唔同, 你又知唔知實際係點做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當你揀好之後, 性質方面仲有再分 B2B B2C C2C  C2B 呢D (呢個通常睇公司)<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\">&quot;想做咩工&quot; 呢個問題一定要搞清楚<br />\n唔係識答要做咩title / 行業就夠<br />\n仲要問自己到底有幾了解自己想做乜<br />\n點樣去搵答案? 準備功夫就係要刨Job Description (JD)<br />\n因為睇得多JD 你先可以知道究竟咩類型既工啱自己, 同埋亦會識得分邊D係伏工</span><br />\n<br />\n利申: 連登仔叫後悔既科, grad左無耐 , FG個時17K -&gt; 20K -&gt; 而家24~26K<br />\n完全0 ot, 福利好, 外資, 而家做得都幾開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔係好高人工, 但都叫不過不失 對得住自己 <br />\n好大原因係因為yr4個時已經開始做緊搵緊資料做career planning"},{"pid":"ba29a4ae35b6df6a350250d2032190807feda24a","tid":2162842,"uid":312363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:31:14.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"7d7a1f6da8b0b779801addf0acc26dc2ae738340","tid":2162842,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:34:51.000Z","msg":